[X] Add macbook_service/requirements.txt (fastapi, uvicorn, docling, pydantic)
[X] Add macbook_service/run.sh startup script with Tailscale IP auto-detection
[X] Add macbook_service/README.md with setup, launchd, and troubleshooting docs
[X] Update Linux app.py: remove torch/docling/unstructured imports
