## Current Task: Few-Shot Learning from Verified POs

### Problem
LLM extraction quality varies per PO format. Once a user verifies a PO is correct, that verified data should teach the model the user's specific format patterns for future extractions.

### Solution
Store verified POs as JSON snapshots in `verified_examples` table. On every new extraction, pass the last 3 verified examples to the LLM as few-shot prompts alongside the raw document text.

### Plan
